ory\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18564,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/03\/17\/call-upon-allah-with-yaqin\/","url_meta":{"origin":32805,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Conviction: Call upon Allah with certainty, without distraction","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 17, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cCall upon Allah with certainty that He will answer you. Know that Allah will not answer the supplication of an unmindful and distracted heart.\" Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3479 Grade: Hasan\u00a0(fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36382,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/05\/28\/allah-angry-no-dua\/","url_meta":{"origin":32805,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Allah angry when He is not asked","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 28, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever never asks from Allah, He will be angry with him.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3373 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064